never delete or change a block
proof of work- mining, lot of computing power into the work

bitcoin- requires the hash of a block to begin with a 
certain amount of zeroes
have to try with a lot of combinations
to create one new block every 10 minutes

to create a block- create a transaction, compute its hash,
and add it to an array

difficulty- 2: block mined: starts with 2 zeroes
increase difficulty to prevent spamming

cryptocurrency- allow multiple transactions in a block
add rewards for miners
virtual money or coins

pending transactions- only one block created every 10 minutes
